that I give a gospel tract to somebody,

00:50:31.979 --> 00:50:33.979
and they're like, hey, somebody else just gave me one.

00:50:33.979 --> 00:50:35.019
In fact, there was a time

00:50:35.019 --> 00:50:36.939
that somebody pulled one off of the counter,

00:50:36.939 --> 00:50:38.619
and they said, yeah, I just got this from somebody else.

00:50:38.619 --> 00:50:39.459
Does it look familiar?

00:50:39.459 --> 00:50:40.939
And I'm like, yeah, it's from our church.

00:50:40.939 --> 00:50:42.379
Hallelujah.

00:50:42.379 --> 00:50:43.459
Praise the Lord.

00:50:43.459 --> 00:50:46.179
When we were there in Idaho,

00:50:46.179 --> 00:50:50.339
a much smaller area as far as population is concerned,

00:50:50.339 --> 00:50:53.059
and for those of you that were there on that trip,

00:50:53.059 --> 00:50:56.019
you remember, and we shared testimony when we got back,

00:50:56.019 --> 00:50:57.739
that there were times that we're passing out

00:50:57.739 --> 00:50:58.779
some of those invitations,

00:50:58.779 --> 00:51:00.179
and there were other people that were nearby,

00:51:00.179 --> 00:51:03.099
and said, yeah, I got one of those earlier this week.

00:51:03.099 --> 00:51:04.579
Praise God.

00:51:04.579 --> 00:51:05.419
Why do we do that?

00:51:05.419 --> 00:51:09.139
Because we're expecting God to use His word.

00:51:09.139 --> 00:51:11.219
Why do we stand and preach the word

00:51:11.219 --> 00:51:13.419
week after week, week after week?

00:51:13.419 --> 00:51:16.059
Because we expect God to use His word

00:51:16.979 --> 00:51:18.539
in the hearts of His people,

00:51:18.539 --> 00:51:20.539
but also in the hearts of lost people.

00:51:21.819 --> 00:51:23.259
And so here we find, again,

00:51:23.259 --> 00:51:26.939
this dual application of do not err.

00:51:26.939 --> 00:51:29.179
When it comes to the situation of sinful temptation,

00:51:29.179 --> 00:51:31.299
don't make excuses.

00:51:31.299 --> 00:51:33.059
Don't excuse behavior.

00:51:33.059 --> 00:51:33.979
It's me.

00:51:35.219 --> 00:51:39.099
It's my own flesh that has the lust,

00:51:39.099 --> 00:51:40.779
and I need to identify that,

00:51:40.779 --> 00:51:42.139
and I need to walk in the Spirit

00:51:42.139 --> 00:51:44.819
so that I will not fulfill the lust of the flesh.

00:51:44.819 --> 00:51:47.459
So long as I excuse and make excuses

00:51:47.459 --> 00:51:49.459
and blame shift and all of those things,

00:51:49.459 --> 00:51:52.659
I'm never gonna have that proper walk with God

00:51:52.659 --> 00:51:55.299
that I'm supposed to have.

00:51:55.299 --> 00:51:56.699
But then when it comes to the situation

00:51:57.459 --> 00:51:58.859
that we read in these last couple of verses

00:51:58.859 --> 00:52:00.659
of our text this morning,

00:52:02.019 --> 00:52:05.339
you didn't pull yourself up by your own bootstraps.

00:52:05.339 --> 00:52:07.979
It's God's blessing and God's favor.

00:52:07.979 --> 00:52:11.739
And everything that we have and everything that we are

00:52:11.739 --> 00:52:14.179
is because of the good hand of God.

00:52:14.179 --> 00:52:15.499
And I believe that.

00:52:15.499 --> 00:52:18.339
And when we believe that and we have that perspective,

00:52:18.339 --> 00:52:20.179
it changes how we live our lives.

00:52:21.619 --> 00:52:23.779
And then we see this thing about the gospel.

00:52:23.779 --> 00:52:26.539
James was saved, praise God,

00:52:27.379 --> 00:52:29.139
but God intends to save a whole harvest,

00:52:29.139 --> 00:52:31.579
not just the first fruits.

00:52:31.579 --> 00:52:33.179
And we're engaged in that work.

00:52:33.179 --> 00:52:36.379
We are, if you're saved this morning,

00:52:36.379 --> 00:52:38.619
part of that harvest,

00:52:38.619 --> 00:52:41.739
but we understand there's more that need to be saved.

00:52:41.739 --> 00:52:44.459
And what a privilege it is to be involved

00:52:44.459 --> 00:52:46.539
in the work of the Lord.

00:52:46.539 --> 00:52:47.379
Let's pray together.

00:52:47.379 --> 00:52:48.459
Father, we love you.

00:52:48.459 --> 00:52:49.819
We thank you so much for loving us.

00:52:49.819 --> 00:52:51.179
Thank you for the word.

00:52:51.179 --> 00:52:53.259
I pray, God, that you would use your word

00:52:53.659 --> 00:52:57.219
in the hearts of your people this morning.

00:52:57.219 --> 00:53:00.499
God, I pray for the one that might be here

00:53:00.499 --> 00:53:03.219
or tuned in via live stream that's not sure of heaven,

00:53:05.019 --> 00:53:07.379
whether it's the first time they've ever heard the gospel

00:53:07.379 --> 00:53:11.619
or maybe they've heard it repeatedly.

00:53:11.619 --> 00:53:16.419
God, I pray that your spirit would work distinctly

00:53:16.419 --> 00:53:18.099
in their heart, draw them to you.

00:53:18.099 --> 00:53:19.619
Lord, would they humble themselves

00:53:19.619 --> 00:53:22.699
and would they accept the free gift of eternal life

00:53:22.699 --> 00:53:25.019
before it's eternally too late.

00:53:25.019 --> 00:53:27.779
God, I pray for those that are born again.

00:53:27.779 --> 00:53:30.419
Lord, help us to have a proper perspective in life.

00:53:30.419 --> 00:53:34.059
Help us to have a biblical worldview

00:53:34.059 --> 00:53:36.779
and a biblical perspective that your word

00:53:36.779 --> 00:53:41.779
would set the course for our thinking and for our behavior

00:53:42.779 --> 00:53:46.539
that God, we would not err in this arena.

00:53:46.539 --> 00:53:49.179
Lord, that we would recognize that everything that we have

00:53:49.179 --> 00:53:51.819
and everything that we are is because of you.

00:53:51.819 --> 00:53:53.179
And that God, we belong to you.

00:53:53.179 --> 00:53:56.179
Everything that we have, we belong to you.

00:53:56.179 --> 00:53:58.939
God, I pray that you'd use us to go forth

00:53:58.939 --> 00:54:01.859
with an expectancy that you will use your word,

00:54:01.859 --> 00:54:03.179
that you will use the gospel.

00:54:03.179 --> 00:54:05.739
It is the power of God unto salvation

00:54:05.739 --> 00:54:07.819
and use us as your people.

00:54:07.819 --> 00:54:11.099
God, I pray that you'd help us now as we've received

00:54:11.099 --> 00:54:13.539
now that we would respond.

00:54:13.539 --> 00:54:15.339
Well, thank you, God, for every decision

00:54:15.339 --> 00:54:16.779
for it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:54:16.779 --> 00:54:18.139
Would you stand with me?

00:54:18.139 --> 00:54:19.419
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:54:19.419 --> 00:54:21.539
Kimberly's gonna play quietly on the piano.

00:54:22.259 --> 00:54:24.219
Maybe you wanna come this morning and thank God

00:54:24.219 --> 00:54:26.459
for every good gift and every perfect gift.

00:54:26.459 --> 00:54:28.619
Maybe you wanna come and ask God to help you

00:54:28.619 --> 00:54:31.979
to be more faithful and fervent and preach in the gospel

00:54:31.979 --> 00:54:34.259
with that heart of expectancy.

00:54:34.259 --> 00:54:35.779
Maybe you're not saved this morning.

00:54:35.779 --> 00:54:37.859
You've never experienced being born again.

00:54:37.859 --> 00:54:40.379
And today is the day of salvation.

00:54:40.379 --> 00:54:42.779
However, the Lord may have spoken to you this morning.

00:54:42.779 --> 00:54:44.139
Would we do business with God

00:54:44.139 --> 00:54:46.179
as Kimberly plays the altars open?

